WEBVTT

01:31.700 --> 01:35.980
[Veil of Shadows]

01:35.980 --> 01:38.980
[Episode 23]

01:58.120 --> 01:58.650
Bai Ze.

01:59.710 --> 02:00.410
What was that?

02:04.510 --> 02:05.260
Ji Can, a Lonescale.

02:06.200 --> 02:06.980
Ji Can?

02:08.400 --> 02:09.420
Unlike your name,

02:10.030 --> 02:10.690
"ji" here

02:11.520 --> 02:12.650
refers to loneliness.

02:15.000 --> 02:16.740
Do you feel lonely right now?

02:20.120 --> 02:20.970
Not just now.

02:23.310 --> 02:24.340
It's always been this way.

02:26.190 --> 02:27.180
Chi Wen's dragon scale,

02:27.180 --> 02:28.340
which you once swallowed,

02:28.840 --> 02:30.020
has been inside you,

02:31.750 --> 02:33.300
feeding on your loneliness

02:33.750 --> 02:34.860
all this time.

02:35.470 --> 02:36.810
Finally, it took form,

02:37.400 --> 02:38.300
becoming a demon.

02:39.400 --> 02:40.620
A demon named Lonescale.

02:42.630 --> 02:43.530
Over the years,

02:44.430 --> 02:45.370
you held high positions

02:45.430 --> 02:46.420
as the Dragon Deity,

02:47.190 --> 02:48.210
beloved by everyone.

02:49.400 --> 02:50.630
But no one really understands

02:50.630 --> 02:51.770
your loneliness.

02:56.750 --> 02:58.210
You stay alone in the Scale Cave,

02:59.750 --> 03:00.770
accompanied

03:02.120 --> 03:03.140
only by your shadow.

03:04.710 --> 03:05.860
Over the years,

03:07.680 --> 03:09.620
your loneliness gave birth to this demon.

03:10.680 --> 03:12.210
It embodies the untold loneliness

03:12.710 --> 03:14.140
deep in your heart.

03:17.150 --> 03:18.180
Throughout the ages,

03:20.120 --> 03:21.740
there have been only two Lonescales.

03:23.120 --> 03:24.650
Because only the loneliest beings

03:25.360 --> 03:27.020
can give birth to this demon.

03:29.870 --> 03:30.580
Two?

03:33.630 --> 03:34.530
Where's the other one?

03:46.560 --> 03:47.460
Do you remember?

03:48.470 --> 03:49.690
Lu Wuyi keeps saying

03:50.190 --> 03:52.140
that you carry a unique fragrance.

03:52.870 --> 03:53.740
Master Dragon Deity.

03:55.960 --> 03:57.900
You have such a special fragrance.

03:59.470 --> 04:01.460
I've never smelled it in the mortal world.

04:02.150 --> 04:03.340
How come

04:04.630 --> 04:06.530
you've obtained a fragrance?

04:08.590 --> 04:09.530
Is it because of him?

04:10.430 --> 04:11.210
Dragon bone,

04:11.590 --> 04:12.340
dragon saliva,

04:12.910 --> 04:14.020
dragon blood, and dragon scale

04:14.430 --> 04:15.370
all carry a fragrance.

04:16.190 --> 04:17.570
Lonescale is essentially a dragon scale

04:18.000 --> 04:19.250
feeding on your loneliness.

04:20.160 --> 04:20.740
Therefore,

04:21.160 --> 04:23.010
it also carries a unique scent.

04:23.800 --> 04:25.300
But this scent

04:26.600 --> 04:28.420
makes people sad,

04:30.070 --> 04:32.740
as if they're hollowed out.

04:34.160 --> 04:35.570
But this fragrance

04:37.360 --> 04:39.060
leaves a hollow ache in the heart,

04:39.390 --> 04:42.300
like a valley full of blooming flowers,

04:42.480 --> 04:44.220
yet utterly devoid of people.

04:44.430 --> 04:45.740
It's like flowers in an empty valley

04:46.310 --> 04:47.450
or thick snow on an ancient temple.

04:48.240 --> 04:49.490
The lonelier you are inside,

04:49.750 --> 04:51.130
the stronger this scent becomes.

04:52.390 --> 04:54.330
Master Dragon Deity, your fragrance

04:55.000 --> 04:55.980
seems to be lighter.

04:57.000 --> 04:59.130
Why is your fragrance fading?

04:59.680 --> 05:00.420
Nonsense.

05:05.190 --> 05:07.420
Then why can't anyone smell it,

05:08.870 --> 05:10.060
including me?

05:10.720 --> 05:11.660
Only those

05:11.660 --> 05:12.980
who truly understand your loneliness

05:14.560 --> 05:15.540
can smell it.

05:19.630 --> 05:20.570
It's true.

05:20.950 --> 05:22.300
I'm not lying to you.

05:25.680 --> 05:26.930
As we approach the end,

05:27.040 --> 05:28.010
things get more unpredictable,

05:28.750 --> 05:30.540
and you grow more hesitant

05:30.800 --> 05:31.420
and hurt.

05:32.800 --> 05:33.420
Right?

05:36.950 --> 05:38.060
I'm not hesitant.

05:39.870 --> 05:40.740
I'm afraid.

05:42.950 --> 05:43.780
I'm scared

05:44.600 --> 05:46.100
that after so many years of struggle,

05:48.070 --> 05:50.370
I'd fail to live up to your expectations

05:52.680 --> 05:53.930
and let you down

05:55.830 --> 05:56.740
in the end.

05:58.190 --> 05:59.570
But you're also scared to succeed.

06:01.070 --> 06:01.570
Aren't you?

06:02.870 --> 06:04.420
Because to reach the end,

06:04.720 --> 06:05.690
you must accept

06:05.750 --> 06:07.010
the fact that you'd lose her.

06:10.070 --> 06:11.780
That's why I cherish

06:11.870 --> 06:13.420
every moment I have with her.

06:14.830 --> 06:16.620
Why are you torturing yourself?

06:16.800 --> 06:17.890
I don't want to lose her.

06:20.390 --> 06:21.490
But it's inevitable.

06:26.000 --> 06:26.930
I have no choice.

06:29.160 --> 06:30.860
But you have to make a choice.

06:32.750 --> 06:33.800
Or you'll be devoured

06:33.800 --> 06:34.810
by Lonescale.

06:36.390 --> 06:37.540
What will happen

06:41.560 --> 06:42.660
if I am devoured?

06:46.680 --> 06:47.370
Master Dragon Deity.

06:57.160 --> 06:57.860
Master Bai Ze.

06:58.600 --> 06:59.490
What brought you here?

07:02.190 --> 07:03.100
How's everything going?

07:04.120 --> 07:04.980
The Spirit-Binding Ring

07:05.680 --> 07:06.980
and the Dragon Deity's Power of Han Ba

07:07.720 --> 07:08.980
were snatched away by Lu Wuyi.

07:12.160 --> 07:13.660
What exactly does she want?

07:14.750 --> 07:15.420
No idea.

07:16.720 --> 07:17.930
She simply vanished.

07:19.430 --> 07:20.980
The Dragon Deity's Power is crucial.

07:21.750 --> 07:22.780
We must find her.

07:27.480 --> 07:29.690
Master, why did your fragrance

07:30.600 --> 07:32.010
suddenly grow so intense?

07:34.750 --> 07:36.010
You also smell it, Commander Li?

07:37.870 --> 07:39.660
I don't think you could smell it before.

07:41.040 --> 07:41.660
That's right.

07:42.830 --> 07:44.540
Lu Wuyi kept mentioning it,

07:46.560 --> 07:47.490
and I've been curious.

07:48.310 --> 07:49.130
I didn't expect

07:50.000 --> 07:51.100
this fragrance

07:51.510 --> 07:53.220
to be so heartbreaking.

07:55.160 --> 07:55.930
It feels like

07:58.240 --> 07:59.540
entering an ancient temple

08:00.240 --> 08:02.250
abandoned in the heavy snow.

08:48.670 --> 08:49.500
I know him.

08:50.150 --> 08:51.450
I've seen him at the Dragon Deity Temple.

08:51.910 --> 08:52.930
He's Master Chi Wen.

08:53.510 --> 08:54.900
The Dragon Deity really descended.

08:55.240 --> 08:56.690
We're saved.

08:57.810 --> 08:58.630
Yes!

08:58.630 --> 08:59.380
Master Chi Wen.

09:00.400 --> 09:01.490
Help us.

09:06.050 --> 09:07.330
Master Chi Wen.

09:08.780 --> 09:10.200
Master Chi Wen.

09:17.080 --> 09:17.810
I know him.

09:18.030 --> 09:19.180
He's Master Chi Wen.

09:19.270 --> 09:20.540
I've seen him at the Dragon Deity Temple.

09:20.750 --> 09:21.420
Master Chi Wen.

09:21.670 --> 09:22.260
Master Chi Wen.

09:22.480 --> 09:23.140
Master Chi Wen.

09:23.200 --> 09:24.540
Please bestow rainfall upon us.

09:24.550 --> 09:25.540
Please help us.

09:25.790 --> 09:26.540
Master Chi Wen.

09:26.870 --> 09:28.140
Please help us.

09:28.270 --> 09:29.540
Please help us.

09:30.670 --> 09:31.730
He is not a Dragon Deity.

09:31.910 --> 09:33.180
He can't help us at all.

09:33.320 --> 09:34.000
We've been worshipping

09:34.000 --> 09:34.780
and admiring him,

09:34.870 --> 09:35.850
but he doesn't do anything.

09:36.000 --> 09:37.610
- Get him. - Get him.

10:07.510 --> 10:08.120
Where's Master Dragon Deity?

10:08.120 --> 10:09.180
- Where is he? - Where did he go?

10:09.690 --> 10:10.640
- He's gone. - Master is gone.

10:11.600 --> 10:12.380
Where did he go?

10:12.790 --> 10:13.560
Where's Master Dragon Deity?

10:27.440 --> 10:28.450
What Ji Ling said is true.

10:29.270 --> 10:30.610
Lu Wuyi deceived us.

10:32.030 --> 10:32.780
You weren't the one

10:32.780 --> 10:34.490
who cast the Word Magic on Mu Long.

10:35.150 --> 10:35.970
It was my sister.

10:37.360 --> 10:37.850
Ji Ling.

10:38.550 --> 10:39.260
I'm sorry.

10:42.120 --> 10:43.090
My name is Mu Long.

10:43.790 --> 10:45.420
My mother named me Mu Long,

10:45.960 --> 10:47.450
which means "admiring dragons."

10:49.120 --> 10:50.140
Our entire family

10:50.750 --> 10:52.020
sees Master Dragon Deity

10:52.200 --> 10:53.730
as an almighty...

10:54.000 --> 10:55.500
They all believed in him.

10:56.000 --> 10:57.420
But I never did.

10:58.390 --> 10:59.330
Because I thought

11:00.320 --> 11:01.540
if there were dragons

11:01.960 --> 11:02.850
in this world

11:03.390 --> 11:04.730
that could eliminate disaster,

11:05.360 --> 11:07.380
then no creature would be suffering.

11:08.320 --> 11:09.260
So I didn't believe in him.

11:10.000 --> 11:10.900
Nor did I worship him.

11:11.750 --> 11:13.690
Therefore, I hated my name.

11:15.320 --> 11:17.060
Is Master Dragon Deity aware

11:17.870 --> 11:19.610
of all the worldly suffering?

11:38.510 --> 11:39.450
But then,

11:40.390 --> 11:42.690
my great-grandmother fell ill after a stroke.

11:43.120 --> 11:44.380
I had no choice.

11:45.030 --> 11:45.450
I...

11:45.750 --> 11:46.060
I...

11:46.080 --> 11:47.210
I had to worship

11:47.240 --> 11:48.450
and beg him.

11:49.150 --> 11:50.780
At that moment, I finally realized

11:50.790 --> 11:52.060
what he tried to show us.

11:52.720 --> 11:54.330
What sustains us through suffering

11:55.120 --> 11:56.090
and helps us defeat evil...

11:56.360 --> 11:57.970
is not the blessing of the deities

11:58.960 --> 12:00.610
but the hope we have.

12:02.600 --> 12:03.570
Here you are.

12:07.480 --> 12:09.020
Lu Wuyi will come.

12:11.120 --> 12:12.660
I have to stop her.

12:13.200 --> 12:14.140
Lu Wuyi will come?

12:15.150 --> 12:15.690
Yes.

12:17.480 --> 12:18.210
I dreamed of it.

12:20.870 --> 12:21.570
And

12:23.720 --> 12:24.660
I was here too.

12:25.080 --> 12:25.930
No.

12:26.840 --> 12:27.690
No.

12:28.750 --> 12:29.450
Ji Ling.

12:29.750 --> 12:30.300
Dream?

12:31.390 --> 12:32.540
Like Ji Ling,

12:32.960 --> 12:34.330
I've also had a similar dream.

12:36.910 --> 12:37.610
In that dream,

12:38.480 --> 12:40.180
you were possessed by Jiu Ying

12:41.360 --> 12:42.850
after gathering all the Dragon Deity's Power.

12:43.120 --> 12:44.500
Jiu Ying manipulated you

12:44.550 --> 12:45.500
to kill Chi Wen.

12:46.320 --> 12:47.930
So Ji Ling is not trustworthy.

12:51.150 --> 12:51.840
But I've also

12:51.840 --> 12:52.840
seen him

12:52.840 --> 12:53.610
in Chi Wen's memory.

12:54.390 --> 12:55.690
His eyes were crystal clear,

12:56.510 --> 12:57.330
free from all impurity.

12:58.120 --> 12:59.500
I'm reluctant to believe

13:00.320 --> 13:01.810
that he covets the dragon throne.

13:03.200 --> 13:03.850
Otherwise,

13:05.000 --> 13:05.750
there wouldn't be

13:05.750 --> 13:07.500
so many outstanding double-flower hunters

13:07.510 --> 13:08.730
who vow to follow him.

13:09.910 --> 13:11.020
This moment

13:11.390 --> 13:13.450
has been repeated countless times.

13:14.910 --> 13:15.850
All of us

13:16.720 --> 13:18.690
have been going back in time over and over.

13:20.200 --> 13:21.140
Those are not dreams,

13:21.750 --> 13:23.660
but what really happened.

13:25.150 --> 13:26.930
It was repeated too many times

13:29.270 --> 13:31.180
and was etched in the depths of our consciousness

13:33.630 --> 13:34.970
like a vague dream.

13:35.580 --> 13:38.060
♪How pitiful, how sad...♪

13:42.510 --> 13:43.500
Now,

13:46.320 --> 13:47.180
I have finally realized

13:49.200 --> 13:50.780
what exactly Wu wanted to do.

13:51.020 --> 13:53.860
♪To go back and see my hometown...♪

13:54.600 --> 13:56.060
The man she's trying to save

13:57.180 --> 13:59.780
♪As I drift farther away...♪

13:59.790 --> 14:00.850
is not Wu Wangyan.

14:03.720 --> 14:04.660
The years are too long,

14:05.670 --> 14:07.450
long enough to change our original intention.

14:10.320 --> 14:11.420
People change.

14:20.390 --> 14:21.690
Ji Ling can lie to me.

14:23.840 --> 14:24.810
But Lu Wuyi

14:25.510 --> 14:26.420
can also lie to you.

14:28.870 --> 14:30.380
One of them

14:31.720 --> 14:33.210
has to be lying.

14:37.320 --> 14:38.380
Wu lied to me.

14:40.550 --> 14:41.570
I lied to her too.

14:41.820 --> 14:43.820
♪In the cold rain, on the mountain...♪

14:43.840 --> 14:44.730
We are

14:46.150 --> 14:47.210
both lying.

14:48.420 --> 14:52.220
♪Heartbroken people are asleep...♪

14:52.270 --> 14:52.930
Ji.

14:54.440 --> 14:55.540
You lied to me.

14:58.840 --> 15:00.500
You've been lying to me.

15:04.020 --> 15:06.820
♪Sever our tie, stop this resentment♪

15:08.140 --> 15:11.260
♪I stole the spring♪

15:11.620 --> 15:14.500
♪To see the mountain flowers bloom with you♪

15:14.940 --> 15:17.540
♪Drink to our heart's content in the wind♪

15:17.700 --> 15:20.500
♪The skeleton holds up the oath♪

15:21.060 --> 15:24.020
♪But the color of my loneliness♪

15:24.220 --> 15:26.940
♪Resembles the setting sun dyeing the shackles♪

15:30.620 --> 15:33.660
♪Sing lightly, a soft chorus♪

15:34.480 --> 15:35.690
So what are you going to do?

15:44.150 --> 15:45.020
No matter what,

15:48.390 --> 15:50.180
I must retrieve the Dragon Deity's Power.

16:01.910 --> 16:02.450
Stop.

16:08.480 --> 16:09.090
Wu.

16:12.360 --> 16:14.140
Why can she activate the Spirit-Binding Ring?

16:18.840 --> 16:20.330
She has the dragon's scent.

16:23.730 --> 16:24.420
How come?

16:28.510 --> 16:29.300
It's the Lonescale.

16:29.910 --> 16:31.420
She has the sacred power of a Lonescale.

16:32.840 --> 16:34.300
The Lonescale is transformed from dragon scales.

16:35.080 --> 16:36.930
The Spirit-Binding Ring was confused by the scent

16:37.360 --> 16:38.730
and recognized her as its master.

16:39.480 --> 16:40.180
But

16:41.150 --> 16:41.970
why does she

16:42.000 --> 16:43.610
carry the scent of a Lonescale?

16:58.030 --> 16:58.660
Wu.

17:01.840 --> 17:02.810
We are still

17:04.790 --> 17:06.610
in a rewind.

17:08.160 --> 17:08.740
Right?

17:19.920 --> 17:21.890
You've been through

17:25.440 --> 17:26.890
countless rewinds,

17:29.350 --> 17:30.740
enduring all the pain

17:33.200 --> 17:35.090
just to save someone.

18:02.750 --> 18:04.090
The person you've wanted to save

18:09.030 --> 18:10.220
has always been me.

18:14.510 --> 18:15.170
Right?

18:22.830 --> 18:23.940
Deception.

18:26.720 --> 18:28.740
Perhaps only lies and deception

18:31.680 --> 18:33.410
can help me save you.

18:35.200 --> 18:35.810
Ji Ling.

18:36.590 --> 18:37.260
Ji Ling.

18:43.680 --> 18:44.410
Ji Ling.

20:05.680 --> 20:06.170
Yes.

20:15.900 --> 20:20.070
[First time]

20:20.070 --> 20:20.960
I have sent Wu Wangyan's body

20:20.960 --> 20:22.260
back to the Formless Moon.

20:23.110 --> 20:23.880
He will be resurrected

20:23.880 --> 20:25.330
from the Primordial Sacred Spring soon.

20:26.750 --> 20:28.130
And Wu Shiguang

20:28.160 --> 20:29.650
is about to slay the dragon.

20:31.000 --> 20:32.980
I have played this game with you for years.

20:35.200 --> 20:36.460
The game is finally settled.

20:37.830 --> 20:39.740
I've accompanied you on this final journey.

20:41.680 --> 20:43.130
Once this heavy rain falls,

20:45.160 --> 20:45.980
my mission

20:48.030 --> 20:49.020
will be completed.

20:56.590 --> 20:58.650
No one can control three demon powers simultaneously.

21:00.310 --> 21:01.570
Your spiritual veins will be torn,

21:04.720 --> 21:05.810
and your soul shattered.

21:06.270 --> 21:07.300
I've made up my mind.

21:09.880 --> 21:10.890
Just let me do it.

21:21.550 --> 21:22.570
By the fox's call,

21:23.480 --> 21:24.540
wrathful sandstorm.

21:46.480 --> 21:47.740
Eastern Purple Lightning,

21:49.000 --> 21:50.220
grant me your power.

21:57.200 --> 21:57.780
Ji Ling.

21:58.640 --> 21:59.260
Ji Ling.

23:11.030 --> 23:11.700
Ji Ling.

23:16.510 --> 23:17.090
Ji Ling.

23:18.480 --> 23:19.330
Is that you?

23:21.750 --> 23:22.740
I'm not Ji Ling.

23:23.880 --> 23:25.570
I'm the demon in him.

23:27.480 --> 23:28.300
A Lonescale.

23:31.750 --> 23:33.260
You should be very familiar

23:35.270 --> 23:36.500
with my scent.

23:40.720 --> 23:41.610
The fragrance.

23:43.400 --> 23:44.170
So it's you.

23:47.350 --> 23:48.850
Are you upset?

23:52.480 --> 23:53.020
Yes.

23:54.640 --> 23:56.090
Do you regret it?

23:56.960 --> 23:58.890
Do you want to start over?

24:00.310 --> 24:00.940
Yes.

24:03.720 --> 24:05.300
I have the ability

24:06.550 --> 24:08.060
to rewind time.

24:09.030 --> 24:11.020
I can take you back in time

24:11.920 --> 24:12.980
to change everything.

24:17.350 --> 24:18.650
Go back in time?

24:21.240 --> 24:22.810
Why do you have this power?

24:24.310 --> 24:25.460
Ji Ling

24:27.590 --> 24:29.130
lived his entire life in remorse.

24:30.000 --> 24:32.090
He had always wanted to go back in time

24:33.270 --> 24:34.540
to change everything.

24:36.680 --> 24:38.020
If I hadn't

24:39.720 --> 24:41.370
run out of sacred power,

24:43.720 --> 24:46.170
I could have saved Yuan Wuhuo's brother.

24:49.070 --> 24:50.850
If I can go back in time

24:52.960 --> 24:54.060
and choose again,

24:58.680 --> 25:00.700
will I still swallow that dragon scale?

25:09.000 --> 25:10.650
Is it snowing in South Mountain now?

25:14.070 --> 25:15.020
In the next life,

25:17.070 --> 25:18.980
be a carefree

25:19.000 --> 25:20.260
blind fox.

25:22.720 --> 25:23.500
It's summer.

25:26.240 --> 25:28.060
There must be plenty of raspberries

25:31.440 --> 25:32.780
by the Yumian Lake now.

25:36.480 --> 25:37.740
All his remorse

25:38.550 --> 25:40.090
turned into an obsession

25:42.070 --> 25:43.810
and was absorbed by the dragon scale.

25:44.440 --> 25:45.890
That's how I came into being.

25:47.310 --> 25:49.020
His hundred years of obsession

25:49.640 --> 25:51.610
gave me the ability to go back in time.

25:53.720 --> 25:55.220
Do you wish to go back in time

25:56.830 --> 25:58.700
to save your beloved one?

25:59.480 --> 26:00.170
Yes, I do.

26:06.720 --> 26:08.740
But I have Jiu Ying fragments in me.

26:11.400 --> 26:12.740
He'll notice it.

26:13.830 --> 26:15.780
The world of rewinds I create

26:17.640 --> 26:19.000
is a closed universe

26:19.000 --> 26:20.410
free from the laws

26:20.440 --> 26:21.540
of the outside world.

26:23.270 --> 26:24.780
Jiu Ying can't monitor you.

26:25.480 --> 26:27.740
You can do whatever you want

26:28.640 --> 26:30.220
without any fear of failure.

26:31.240 --> 26:33.060
You can do it over and over again

26:35.110 --> 26:35.780
as long as...

26:38.440 --> 26:39.300
As long as what?

26:40.680 --> 26:41.940
As long as your physical form

26:42.160 --> 26:43.300
can withstand it.

26:44.720 --> 26:45.780
Each rewind

26:46.510 --> 26:48.650
rewrites the past

26:49.240 --> 26:51.460
