37:08.940 --> 37:12.580
♪I call for you, my only one...♪

37:16.360 --> 37:17.210
Wait for me.

37:20.550 --> 37:21.250
Wait for me.

37:25.630 --> 37:27.170
I've tried a million ways

37:30.960 --> 37:33.060
and experienced unimaginable hardships.

37:35.400 --> 37:36.130
In the end,

37:37.880 --> 37:38.980
I realized...

37:39.550 --> 37:40.860
If you take Ji Ling's ring,

37:41.880 --> 37:43.170
he can't activate his demon power

37:44.230 --> 37:45.980
and won't be able to sacrifice himself.

37:47.670 --> 37:48.170
No.

37:51.030 --> 37:52.420
I've tried it.

38:05.480 --> 38:06.170
Why?

38:06.420 --> 38:09.000
[Twenty-sixth rewind]

38:09.000 --> 38:10.340
Why doesn't it work?

38:13.000 --> 38:14.380
Taking the ring alone

38:15.150 --> 38:16.940
doesn't change Ji Ling's fate.

38:17.960 --> 38:19.340
I must relieve this drought

38:20.630 --> 38:22.130
with the Dragon Deity's Power.

38:23.760 --> 38:24.250
No.

38:25.480 --> 38:26.020
No.

38:28.280 --> 38:29.020
Why not?

38:30.070 --> 38:31.460
Once the drought is relieved,

38:32.000 --> 38:33.820
The Dragon Deity's Power will dissipate.

38:34.190 --> 38:35.460
It will dissipate?

38:37.000 --> 38:37.900
The Dragon Deity's Power

38:38.630 --> 38:39.940
breaks through all the barriers

38:39.960 --> 38:40.980
and removes all spells.

38:41.550 --> 38:43.380
Didn't Xiaowei lift the Fox-Allure Spell

38:43.480 --> 38:44.250
for the people of Luo'an

38:44.280 --> 38:45.650
with the Dragon Deity's Power?

38:47.760 --> 38:49.210
Lu Wuyi doesn't just want to

38:50.000 --> 38:51.060
relieve the drought.

38:52.070 --> 38:53.380
She also wants to save Ji Ling.

38:55.590 --> 38:56.540
The drought in Luo'an

38:56.630 --> 38:57.290
is destined

38:57.360 --> 38:58.980
to be resolved with Ji Ling's sacrifice.

39:00.440 --> 39:02.020
No matter how many rewinds she attempts,

39:02.800 --> 39:03.650
she can't change

39:03.670 --> 39:05.090
the long-written ending.

39:05.960 --> 39:06.880
If she forcibly

39:06.880 --> 39:08.730
relieves the drought with the Dragon Deity's Power,

39:09.920 --> 39:10.650
she'd be intervening

39:10.670 --> 39:11.920
with Ji Ling's destiny

39:11.920 --> 39:12.860
against the will of heaven.

39:14.280 --> 39:15.170
The Dragon Deity's Power

39:16.400 --> 39:17.860
will naturally dissipate.

39:19.480 --> 39:21.210
Then our long-standing plan...

39:22.480 --> 39:23.060
Wu.

39:25.000 --> 39:25.540
No.

39:25.920 --> 39:26.460
Don't.

39:26.960 --> 39:27.540
Wuyi.

39:28.110 --> 39:28.690
Don't.

39:29.920 --> 39:30.540
Don't.

39:34.880 --> 39:35.690
I insist.

39:38.630 --> 39:39.170
Xiaowei.

39:39.760 --> 39:40.800
Ms. Yu is too badly injured.

39:40.800 --> 39:41.820
She's beyond saving.

39:42.400 --> 39:43.840
You will defy the will of heaven

39:43.840 --> 39:44.540
if you save her

39:44.550 --> 39:45.460
with the Dragon Deity's Power.

39:46.070 --> 39:47.420
You will be reduced to nothing.

39:47.880 --> 39:48.940
I insist.

39:51.360 --> 39:52.730
Even if you resent me,

39:53.920 --> 39:55.650
and even if I'm reduced to nothing,

39:57.190 --> 39:58.420
I want you alive.

40:02.000 --> 40:03.020
I won't let you die.

40:23.550 --> 40:25.290
I have seen through your moves

40:25.840 --> 40:27.420
in my countless rewinds.

40:27.960 --> 40:29.290
Your spells can't contain me.

40:30.630 --> 40:32.420
My sacred power has surpassed yours.

40:33.760 --> 40:34.980
You can't stop me.

40:50.320 --> 40:51.540
I have no sacred power.

40:53.230 --> 40:54.860
You have my ring.

40:58.590 --> 41:00.380
But I must stop you.

41:03.920 --> 41:04.650
Wu.

41:07.670 --> 41:09.060
Don't do this for me.

41:11.400 --> 41:12.130
It's not worth it.

41:14.590 --> 41:15.420
Ji Ling.

41:17.510 --> 41:18.610
Let go.

41:38.150 --> 41:38.860
Wuyi.

41:39.550 --> 41:40.690
Dreamfall.

42:03.440 --> 42:04.610
Thank you

42:05.320 --> 42:06.820
for getting rid of them for me.

42:15.920 --> 42:17.650
Hand over the Dragon Deity's Power of Han Ba,

42:18.630 --> 42:19.420
and I will spare you.

42:21.800 --> 42:22.900
Yuan Wuhuo.

42:41.190 --> 42:42.210
You've been hiding for ages.

42:44.110 --> 42:44.900
Finally, you can't help

42:44.920 --> 42:46.020
but show up.

42:47.320 --> 42:48.770
Since you knew it was me,

42:49.630 --> 42:50.770
why didn't you point it out?

42:52.630 --> 42:53.500
You know

42:55.320 --> 42:57.610
what people become after they go through

42:59.110 --> 43:00.340
