43:30.070 --> 43:31.170
and Li Jie

43:33.230 --> 43:34.540
are insignificant.

43:36.670 --> 43:37.900
Why should I care?

43:41.000 --> 43:44.340
Triple-flower paints the day. All things live and perish.

43:44.360 --> 43:45.900
Before me, all becomes clear.

43:46.440 --> 43:47.130
Appear.

43:58.150 --> 43:59.170
Triple-flower?

44:13.780 --> 44:14.940
♪It's your light♪

44:15.140 --> 44:17.020
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

44:17.180 --> 44:20.300
♪That set the night alight♪

44:20.660 --> 44:27.180
♪And lead me through the fight♪

44:28.940 --> 44:30.820
♪Jade in the lake, sand in my hand♪

44:31.260 --> 44:35.700
♪Let bitter seeds grow, let fate bloom♪

44:36.500 --> 44:38.180
♪Face in the mirror, veiled in mist♪

44:38.340 --> 44:43.740
♪Till snow has kissed dark hair to white♪

44:44.500 --> 44:49.900
♪Night lamp burning by the old table♪

44:52.220 --> 44:58.260
♪Stitch by stitch, mending moonlight♪

44:59.220 --> 45:01.380
♪The dancing light, the shattered wave♪

45:01.660 --> 45:06.500
♪Are all my helpless, drifting haze♪

45:06.860 --> 45:09.180
♪The boiling frost, the stubborn stare♪

45:09.380 --> 45:14.460
♪Are all the pride I'll never wear♪

45:14.700 --> 45:16.700
♪Your shoulder, your tear-bright eyes♪

45:16.980 --> 45:21.340
♪Are the strength that lifts my dreams to the skies♪

45:22.340 --> 45:29.300
♪Stay with me, let's gaze above♪

45:45.860 --> 45:48.820
♪Nowhere to rest, nowhere to hide♪

45:49.900 --> 45:53.300
♪Bare in body yet boundless inside♪

45:54.100 --> 45:56.620
♪Nothing to seek, nothing to erase♪

45:56.860 --> 45:59.940
♪Like water gone, like the formless moon♪

46:00.340 --> 46:02.660
♪Let every dream and wild desire♪

46:03.180 --> 46:07.580
♪Forge the edge that lifts us higher♪

46:07.820 --> 46:09.980
♪Bells through endless time, sun and moon alike in shine♪

46:10.380 --> 46:15.340
♪Love and hate all earn their crown♪

46:15.580 --> 46:16.740
♪It's your light♪

46:16.940 --> 46:18.780
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

46:18.980 --> 46:22.100
♪That set the night alight♪

46:22.860 --> 46:32.300
♪And lead me sailing afar♪
